> Sorry for late review @xiejiajun Does scala 2.12 also need the same change ?
@zjffdu ,  I read the code in the Scala 2.12.x branch, it seems to only support `jvm-1.8`, and the default  target version of  jvm in the  Scala 2.12.x branch is already `jvm-1.8`.

